text: Tiantangbao is a station on Line 2 of Chongqing Rail Transit in Chongqing Municipality, China.http://www.cqmetro.cn It is located in the Dadukou District. It opened in 2014. ==References== Category:Railway stations in Chongqing Category:Railway stations in China opened in 2014 Category:Chongqing Rail Transit stations
